Different NVIDIA graphics cards are based on different hardware 
architectures and certain frameworks may not work on older
generations.


# Fields

* name
* compute_capability

# Actions

## Add hardware

requires:

  * name
  * compute_capability

## Update harware

partial update of any of these fields:

  * name
  * compute_capability


## Delete hardware

requires:

  * name


## Links

* [Hardware support](https://docs.nvidia.com/deploy/cuda-compatibility/index.html#support-hardware)

